        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to generate a report of active energy account meters. It retrieves a list of meters associated with active accounts, including details such as facility information, account numbers, meter numbers, tariff rates, and agency information. The procedure also logs the report usage for auditing purposes."
